CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1945, pg. 9 reads: " Discussing Funds For Furnishings - Members of the Centre Avenue YWCA Funds for Furnishings Project Committee talk it over at a recent report meeting. It was decided at this meeting to extend the campaign through March.  About $2,000 has been raised do date. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Members of the Funds for Furnishings Project Committee, including two women wearing dark dresses with light colored collars, standing in back, gathered around large table with documents, in Centre Avenue YWCA, another version
